OL,3,CSainsbury's and Argos to hire around
OL,4,C19,000 extra workers for Christmas
OL,6,FSainsbury's and Argos are to hire
OL,7,Faround 19,000 staff to help serve a
OL,8,Fsurge in shoppers over the key festive
OL,9,Fseason.
OL,11,FThe two brands, which are both part of
OL,12,Fthe Sainsbury's group, launched the
OL,13,Frecruitment drive on Monday for a raft
OL,14,Fof roles including serving customers,
OL,15,Fdeliveries and replenishing shelves.
OL,17,FIt has opened applications for 17,000
OL,18,Fseasonal roles at Sainsbury's and
OL,19,F2,000 across Argos.
