OL,3,CSainsbury's and Argos to hire around
OL,4,C19,000 extra workers for Christmas
OL,6,FIt said the extra staff members will
OL,7,Fbe essential in keeping stores, online
OL,8,Fservices and deliveries running
OL,9,Fsmoothly over the festive period.
OL,11,FIn-store and warehouse fulfilment
OL,12,Fworkers will be paid between #12.60
OL,13,Fand #13.85 per hour, varying based on
OL,14,Fspecific roles and locations.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, Argos drivers will receive
OL,17,Fbetween #13.60 and #14.85 per hour,
OL,18,Fwith Sainsbury's drivers receiving
OL,19,Fbetween #14.10 and #15.35 per hour.
