OL,3,CSainsbury's and Argos to hire around
OL,4,C19,000 extra workers for Christmas
OL,6,FThe retail firm, which has almost 600
OL,7,Fsupermarkets and more than 800
OL,8,Fconvenience stores, said it will
OL,9,Fprovide free food during shifts.
OL,11,FIt will also offer eligible workers a
OL,12,F10% discount at Sainsbury's and Argos,
OL,13,Fwith this rising to 15% every Friday
OL,14,Fand Saturday at Sainsbury's, and on
OL,15,Fpayday at Argos.
