OL,3,CSainsbury's and Argos to hire around
OL,4,C19,000 extra workers for Christmas
OL,6,FTracey Clements, chief retail,
OL,7,Flogistics and supply chain officer at
OL,8,FSainsbury's, said: "Christmas is when
OL,9,Fcustomers count on us most and our
OL,10,Fcolleagues play a vital role in making
OL,11,Fit truly special.
OL,13,F"We're looking forward to welcoming
OL,14,Fthousands of new team members to help
OL,15,Fus deliver great-tasting festive
OL,16,Fproducts, unbeatable value and
OL,17,Fbrilliant service across our stores,
OL,18,Ffulfilment centres and out on the
OL,19,Froad, delivering to customers in
OL,20,Fcommunities across the UK.
